    "setting": {
        "title": "禁用状态",
        "order": 2
    },
    "catalogs": [],
    "contents": "<p>给<code>ScrollSelect</code>添加<code>disabled</code>属性，可以禁用整个组件；给组件添加<code>disable</code>函数用来禁用单独的数据项。本例中，我们可以传入<code>disable</code>函数来禁用闰年选项</p>\n",
    "index": 115,
    "highlighted": [
        {
            "language": "vdt",
            "content": "<pre><code class=\"hljs jsx\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> ScrollSelect <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">'kpc/components/scrollSelect'</span>;\n\n<span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">ScrollSelect</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">data</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">{{</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">self.generateData</span> }}\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">v-model</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"value\"</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">disable</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">{{</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">self.disable</span> }}\n/&gt;</span></span></code></pre>"
        },
        {
            "language": "js",
            "content": "<pre><code class=\"hljs js\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> Intact <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">'intact'</span>;\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> template <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">'./index.vdt'</span>;\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"hljs-class\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">Intact</span> </span>{\n    @Intact.template()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">static</span> template = template;\n\n    defaults() {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> {\n            <span class=\"hljs-attr\">value</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">2018</span>\n        };\n    }\n\n    generateData(value) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> start = value - <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>;\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Array</span>.apply(<span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, {<span class=\"hljs-attr\">length</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>})\n            .map(<span class=\"hljs-function\">(<span class=\"hljs-params\">v, i</span>) =&gt;</span> {\n                <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> year = start + i; \n                <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> {\n                    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">label</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">`<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${year}</span>年`</span>,\n                    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">value</span>: year\n                };\n            });\n    }\n\n    disable(value) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 排除闰年</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> value % <span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span> === <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> &amp;&amp; (value % <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span> !== <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> || value % <span class=\"hljs-number\">400</span> === <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>);\n    }\n}</code></pre>"
        }
    ]
}